      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THINKING OF YOU (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 6th and beaten 10 lengths at Murray Bridge Straight (17.67). Has a strong record here at this journey including three wins. The form from her last run stacks up well. Tough to beat if on-song. MINH JACK (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.69) in a Grade 5 at Murray Bridge. Has a good record at this journey. Has the ability to give this a shake. OUR BELLA ROSE (1) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (20.20) at this track in a Grade 6 over 342m. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. CABAO NICKEL (7) raced handy last time and scored. Right in the mix.",
